-- Emerging Global Advisors Expands Beyond BRICs in ETF
-- B y   Y e   X i e
-- 2012-08-15T13:38:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-15/emerging-global-expands-beyond-brics-in-new-exchange-traded-fund.html
Emerging Global Advisors is offering
two new exchange-traded funds, including one that targets stocks
in  developing countries  outside of Brazil,  Russia , India and
China.  The EGShares Beyond BRICs tracks an  INDXX LLC index  that
invests in 50 stocks in 15 emerging-market countries including
 Chile ,  Malaysia ,  Mexico  and  Turkey , the New York-based company
said in a statement. The EGShares Domestic Demand ETF will
invest in consumer stocks in  emerging markets .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ye Xie in  New York  at 
